<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-13-1049 </DOCNO><TEXT>We show how chiral anomalies arise in the Fokker-Planck formulation ofstochastic quantization. Starting from a noise correlation function whichis non-local in real space-time, a gauge invariantly regularized Fokker-PlanckHamiltonian is derived and used to compute the anomaly.</TEXT></DOC>